* To run on locally on http://localhost:8080
	python3 -m http.server 8080

* To minify JS use Google Closure compiler (https://developers.google.com/closure/compiler/)

	curl https://closure-compiler.googlecode.com/git/contrib/externs/jquery-1.8.js > jquery-1.8.js
	java -jar compiler.jar --js `echo $(ls assets/js/*.js)` --js_output_file assets/js/all.min.js --externs jquery-1.8.js

* To minify HTML using HTML Compressor (https://code.google.com/p/htmlcompressor)
	
	curl https://htmlcompressor.googlecode.com/files/htmlcompressor-1.5.3.jar > htmlcompressor.jar
	java -jar htmlcompressor.jar -t html index.html > index.min.html

* To minify CSS using YUI Compressor (http://yui.github.io/yuicompressor/)

	sudo apt-get install yui-compressor
	java -jar /usr/share/yui-compressor/yui-compressor.jar -o '.css$:.min.css' ./assets/css/*.css